#: templates/cashbook/about.html:33
#, python-format
msgid ""
"It's free. There's no signup funnel, no usage limit, no upsell pop-up. The "
"free Community edition of %(link)s runs Cashbook out of the box, and your "
"data lives on your own server (or on the demo server, if this is the public "
"demo)."
msgstr ""
"See on tasuta. Pole registreerumislehtrit, kasutuslimiiti ega müügihüpikuid."
" %(link)s tasuta Community väljaanne sisaldab Kassaraamatut kohe ja sinu "
"andmed asuvad sinu enda serveris (või demoserveris, kui see on avalik demo)."

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:37
msgid "What you can do here"
msgstr "Mida siin teha saab"

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:39
msgid "Record cash-in and cash-out from a single screen."
msgstr "Märgi raha sissetulek ja väljaminek ühelt ekraanilt."

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:40
msgid "Issue invoices and send them as PDFs."
msgstr "Väljasta arveid ja saada neid PDF-idena."

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:41
msgid "Send quotes and convert accepted ones into invoices."
msgstr "Saada hinnapakkumisi ja muuda vastuvõetud pakkumised arveteks."

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:42
msgid "See running totals — Cash in, Cash out, Net — for the current month."
msgstr ""
"Vaata jooksvaid kokkuvõtteid — raha sisse, raha välja, neto — jooksva kuu "
"kohta."

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:43
msgid "Export everything to CSV for your accountant."
msgstr "Ekspordi kõik oma raamatupidaja jaoks CSV-sse."

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:48
#, fuzzy
msgid "What's"
msgstr "Mis on"

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:48
msgid "not"
msgstr "mitte"

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:48
msgid "here, intentionally"
msgstr "siin, tahtlikult"

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:50
msgid "No bank feeds. (Coming with the Business edition.)"
msgstr "Pangavooge pole. (Tulevad Business väljaandega.)"

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:51
msgid "No BAS or PAYG lodgement. (Coming with the Pro edition.)"
msgstr "BAS-i ega PAYG esitamist pole. (Tuleb Pro väljaandega.)"

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:52
msgid ""
"No bills/AP, no payroll, no double-entry journals you have to think about."
msgstr ""
"Pole ostuarveid/AP-d, palgaarvestust ega kahekordse kirjendamise kandeid, "
"millele peaks mõtlema."

#: templates/cashbook/about.html:58
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The ATO requires that issued invoices stay in the audit trail. So Cashbook "
"doesn't have a \"delete\" button for sent invoices — only %(void)s, which "
"writes a reversal record. If you've never thought about that distinction, "
"that's exactly the point: the right thing to do is the only button you'll "
"see."
msgstr ""
"ATO nõuab, et väljastatud arved jääksid auditijälge. Seetõttu pole "
"Kassaraamatus saadetud arvete jaoks \"kustuta\" nuppu — ainult %(void)s, mis"
" kirjutab tühistuskande. Kui sa pole kunagi sellele eristusele mõelnud, siis"
" täpselt selles ongi mõte: õige valik on ainus nupp, mida näed."

